{"tid":1703306,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"視障人士趕沙田尾班車不果 遭港鐵職員推跌在地","createTime":"2019-11-10T08:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T14:14:54.000Z","uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"75f535735a0a493f06036dbf94b3b9d1c2af440b","tid":1703306,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"視障人士趕沙田尾班車不果<br />\n遭港鐵職員推跌在地<br />\n<br />\n【沙田即時】(15:00) 大批示威者在下午近3時破壞沙田港鐵站，港鐵即宣佈沙田站即時關閉。在落閘關站期間，一名視障女士欲趕乘最後一班列車，惟職員不讓入閘，並要求她離開閘口。<br />\n<br />\n由於港鐵職員沒有任何指示離開方向，亦沒有人攙扶她，一度在混亂中被港鐵職員推跌。港鐵職員馬上把鐵閘落下，令該視障女士未能離開，她之後更直接平躺在地上阻止港鐵落閘。<br />\n<br />\n大批市民見狀及後趕至，並斥港鐵職員：「有冇人性㗎你地！」之後有兩名市民加入阻止落閘﹐港鐵職員才把已下了一半的鐵閘重開，並讓該名女士步出。她因受到職員的推撞後一度感到不適，需要服用哮喘藥。<br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWO8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=e56fa63c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n投稿／廣告： info@inmediahk.net<br />\n定額捐款： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2W46Sy2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W46Sy2&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWO8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=49b8a9f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2W46Sy2</a><br />\nPaypal 單次捐款：<a href=\"http://paypal.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.me%2Finmediahknet&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWO8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=d7b318b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">paypal.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jx0NHoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjx0NHoC.jpg&h=d2118641&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvRtrQi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvRtrQi.jpg&h=305ef524&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XPnwgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XPnwgZ.jpg&h=9a27aa6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},